s. Moreover, because it does not require gold-standard references, CogniEval supports open-domain, zero-shot evaluation, making it scalable across domains. Ultimately, CogniEval redefines explanation evaluation as a transparent, context-sensitive, and cognitively faithful process—one that mirrors how humans actually assess understanding rather than merely approximating textual similarity.",
